CHAPTER ______
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Howard County – Sheriff and State’s Attorney – Compensation
3 Ho. Co. 13–26
4 FOR the purpose of altering the annual salary of the Sheriff of Howard County and the
5 annual salary of the State’s Attorney for Howard County; and generally relating to
6 the Howard County Sheriff and the State’s Attorney for Howard County.
7 BY repealing and reenacting, with amendments,
8 Article – Courts and Judicial Proceedings
9 Section 2–327(b)
